children.name: Verify Product Added To Shopping Cart SuccessFully
When user mouse hover on Currency Dropdown and click on it
And User mouse hover on £Pound Sterling and click on it
When User mouse hover on Desktops tab and click on it
And User click on Show All Desktops Option
And User click on sort By Position Name: A to Z
And User select the product "HTC Touch HD"
Then User should navigate to the product page and see text for "HTC Touch HD"
And User enter the Qty require as "1"
And User click on Add to cart button
Then User should able to verify the message Success: You have added "HTC Touch HD" to your shopping cart!
And user click on Link Shopping Cart display into success message
Then User should able to verify the product name "HTC Touch HD"
Then User should able to verify the Model "Product 1"
Then User should able to verify the Total "£74.73"
